column2: "Hey there. Are you on a quest, or here on some mission?"
"I came here to exterminate Darkers, but I've become kind of discouraged."
"I ran into some Darkers, but rather than attack me, it looked like they were searching for something."
"I defeated as many as I could, but some still got away. They may still be searching in that area."
"Those Darkers, it almost looked as if they were being lead around. It was really odd."
"But I guess Darkers being weird is nothing new."
